description:
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for a Speciality Doctor to join our well-established Medical team based at Basildon Hospital (BTUH), based within the Acute Medical Unit (AMU)/Medical same day emergency care unit (SDEC).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is an exciting time to join BTUH, with the Trust taking steps to up-skill all staff and embark on a 5-10 year transformational journey. As part of this the AMU/SDEC team are leading the way in driving transformational clinical change.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDr Fawad Ali,Job titleLead Consultant, Medical SDECEmail addressfawad.ali@btuh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
